des: Dry Cleaning and Laundry becomes easier with pickup and delivery dry cleaning and laundry services. Just say 'Alexa, open voice dry cleaner dot com' to get started! Now you can tell voice dry cleaner dot com you are on your way so they can have your clothes ready by the time you get there! Just say, 'Alexa, tell voice dry cleaner dot com I am on my way' to let voice dry cleaner dot com know you are on your way!
